{
  "title": "Slow Cooked Mediterranean Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A rich and indulgent Mediterranean dish featuring tender lamb and flavorful spices, slow cooked to perfection in a stone-bowl-dolsot",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
